name: Welcome Teia Contract _
description:
Hello world 

We are pleased to announce the birth of a healthy, bouncing baby Teia, as of the 20th of March 2022. 

Time to celebrate the amazing teamwork from a group of talented people dedicated to the ideal of a decentralised marketplace and a home. 

 

Now the fun really begins
